snippet.title: Pokémon But I Can't Stop SLIDING (Pokemon Emerald Slide Release - Ice Tile Physics Everywhere)
snippet.description:
Here is the first official Team Aqua's Hideout Romhack: Pokemon Emerald Slide. It is probably one of the goofiest hacks to ever exist. You will find links to download the patch on my Discord below. If you would like to learn how to create Romhacks like this, subscribe to my channel and check out our tutorials, it has never been easier to get into romhacking than it is right now. 

Link To Discord: https://discord.gg/hX3a63RYzZ


#romhack #pokemonemerald #decomp
